title: VICTORIAN Studio avail 8/15 or 9/1
posting_body: ["If you're looking for privacy and charm, this could be the home for you.", "You'll have your own spacious living room/bedroom (15' x 24') with private bath, kitchen and foyer located on the top floor of my 1897 home on Oakland Avenue in south Minneapolis.", "We'll share the laundry, entrance and utility costs which are split 50/50.", 'The average over the past year has been $170/month including Internet access.', "There's also plenty of storage available.", 'Unfortunately, NO pets are allowed.', '(Furniture in photos is not included.)', "In the summer you can relax on the back porch and enjoy the beautiful flower and shrub garden, and you're welcome to help if you'd like.", "I'm a non-smoker and quiet person who recycles fiercely and works at being a green person, and I hope to get the same from you.", 'Rent is $850/month for a single tenant or $1200 for 2; first month and security deposit are due up front.', "I also require last month's rent in advance but this can be prorated over several months.", 'I do require a one year lease.', 'PLEASE RESPOND with 5 years rent and employment history, and with current income.', 'Please tell me why you are moving.', 'This is a very desirable location so many people want to see it.', 'We don’t want to waste your time or ours if you won’t qualify.', 'Thanks for your cooperation!', 'REQUIREMENTS TO MEET:', '- Gross income 3 times the rent that you can document', '- 5 years stable rent and employment history', '- Cell phone with text and photo transmission capability', '- Email capable', 'Please respond by email with above requests.']
